                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.256A8.967 8.967 0 016 18c2.295 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.256A8.967 8.967 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#4B5563] mb-2">Blog & Ressources</h3>
                <p class="text-[#6B7280] text-sm">Partagez vos expériences, échangez des conseils et découvrez des articles inspirants.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#E5E0D8] p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#A7C7E7]/20 text-[#A7C7E7] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
