                <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-[#E5E7EB] bg-white text-[#6B7280] font-medium hover:bg-[#F5F1EB] focus:outline focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#A7C7E7]">Nous contacter</a>
